#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.cumprod"
msgstr "# triton.language.cumprod"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.cumprod` 计算输入tensor沿指定轴的累积乘积，返回累积乘积结果。"
msgstr "Introduction: `triton.language.cumprod` computes the cumulative product of the input tensor along a specified axis, returning the cumulative product result."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.cumprod(input, axis=0, reverse=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | 输入tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | 沿着哪个维度进行累积乘积操作，默认为0 |\n"
"| `reverse` | `bool` | 如果为True，沿反方向进行累积乘积操作 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|-------------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | Input tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | The dimension along which to perform the cumulative product operation, default is 0 |\n"
"| `reverse` | `bool` | If True, performs the cumulative product operation in the reverse direction |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:14
msgid "`cumprod` 函数计算沿指定轴的累积乘积（前缀乘积）。例如，对于输入 `[a, b, c, d]`，累积乘积结果为 `[a, a*b, a*b*c, a*b*c*d]`。"
msgstr "The `cumprod` function computes the cumulative product (prefix product) along a specified axis. For example, for the input `[a, b, c, d]`, the cumulative product result is `[a, a*b, a*b*c, a*b*c*d]`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:16
msgid "当 `reverse=True` 时，计算反向累积乘积：`[a*b*c*d, b*c*d, c*d, d]`。"
msgstr "When `reverse=True`, compute the reverse cumulative product: `[a*b*c*d, b*c*d, c*d, d]`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumprod.md:18
msgid "与 `cumsum` 不同，`cumprod` 没有 `dtype` 参数，因此在使用时需要注意数据类型的溢出问题，特别是对于整数类型的累积乘积。"
msgstr "Unlike `cumsum`, `cumprod` does not have a `dtype` parameter, so attention must be paid to data type overflow issues when using it, especially for cumulative products of integer types."

